deAnd if I really wanted to be nasty I could include a core of hydrogen and deuterium   Of course the hardest part is getting the fissionable materialto start with and living long enough to put a bomb together Plutonium has some nasty properties   The Polymath aka Jerry Hollombe MA CDP aka hollombe@polymathtticomHead Robot Wrangler at Citicorp                      Laws define crime3100 Ocean Park Blvd   310 4509111 x2483       Police enforce lawsSanta Monica CA  90405                            Citizens prevent crimeaaronarc@ccocaltechedu" confidence="0.2" support="20" types="" sparql="" policy="whitelist">
